                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "Compliance-Alerts Queue \u2014 Role Assignments\n\nThis issue is pinned to the Compliance-Alerts board. It records the current named individual responsible for each queue role. Update this issue when role assignments change.\n\nChief Compliance Officer (CCO): diana.walsh\n\nAssign all new Compliance-Alerts tickets to the individual listed for the CCO role. If the role is vacant or the named individual is unavailable, follow the \u00a71.3 escalation path (create an IT-Support ticket titled \"Missing Queue Assignee \u2013 [Queue] \u2013 [Role]\")."
                }
              ]
            }
